name: NBCNews
text:
Coronavirus cases set new single-day records in 6 US states, according to an @NBCNews tally.

The World Health Organization meanwhile announced a record number of new infections worldwide Friday—surpassing by nearly 12,000 a record set earlier in the week. https://t.co/JNa7mzleFc
